data.description: Absolutely adorable single story home in the desirable neighborhood of Viewpoint: Offering 1,407 sq. ft. with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on an oversized lot with a 2.5 car garage. This home has a fantastic split floor plan for privacy, open dining to great room with a cozy fireplace. Spacious, level yard on over 1/4 acre with a huge 12x16 tool shed that is heated and cooled. New appliances, new A/C, new furnace, new water heater. Super cute and clean with laminate wood looking flooring, tile and berber carpet. Quiet neighborhood with a nearby park, shopping, dining and entertainment. HOA is only $69/year!
